                    Are you looking for career guidance?
                </h3>
                <div class="row">
                    <p class="p-3 description">
                        We are a team of IITians who have gone through the same process of JOSAA, and we are well aware
                        of the confusion while filling the preferences, due to availability of multiple options and lack
                        of complete information. And therefore, we have a team of Education and Exam counselors who
