                    Getting Started
                </h3>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="description col-12">
                        <h5>Step1 (Payment)</h5>
                        <p class="p-3">
                            <strong>
                                Case - 1)
                            </strong>
                            If you have a referral code then go to <a href="/kmc/referral">this</a> page and pay the
                            joining fee. <br />
                            <strong>
                                Case - 2)
                            </strong>
                            If you don't have a referral code, then directly pay using the below payment
                            links.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="description col-12">
                        <h5>Step2 (Signing Up)</h5>
                        <p class="p-3">
                            Once you pay the fee, you will be redirected to the <a
                                href="https://kmc.gradeazy.com/">kmc.gradeazy.com</a> where you need to singup using the
